    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a bit sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it. This car is in absolute showroom condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one and it still has that brand-new feel. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. If you're looking for something that\u2019s been meticulously cared for and is ready to hit the road today, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
