    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade 2008 BMW M3 (E92) featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This specimen boasts a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and is finished in Alpine White over Fox Red Novillo leather. The high-revving power unit maintains its factory-spec 8,400 RPM redline with surgical precision, benefiting from documented preventive rod bearing replacement and updated throttle body actuators. The chassis is absolute, featuring the M Variable Differential Lock and EDC-equipped suspension for unparalleled lateral dynamics. Zero evidence of subframe fatigue or VANOS rattle. The exterior retains its original factory clear coat with consistent paint depth micron readings across all panels. Inside, the Novillo leather bolsters show no compression or epidermal wear, reflecting a true collector-grade cabin. This is a turnkey, investment-quality icon for the discerning purist.",
